A_{n, \lambda}=\begin {pmatrix} \lambda & -1\\ -1 & \lambda & -1\\  & -1 & \lambda & -1\\ & & \ddots& \ddots &\ddots \\ & & & &  -1 \\  & & & -1  & \lambda &   \end{pmatrix}
